A toolkit for verifiably authentic photos
In an era of AI-generated images and sophisticated editing tools, proving that a photo is real matters more than ever. ZCAM gives developers the tools to build authentic images directly into their apps.
Succinct&#x27;s ZCAM SDK provides a full ecosystem for taking, managing and verifying authentic photos.
Whether you&#x27;re building for journalism, insurance, identity verification, or any use case where image authenticity matters, these docs will help you get started.

